snippet.title: Fermat primality test (Prime Adventure Part 10)
snippet.description:
Fermat Primality test, rough outline of how & why it works. 

Note, this doesn't assume strong background in modular arithmetic, for those details please see full lesson here:
https://www.khanacademy.org/math/applied-math/cryptography/modarithmetic/a/what-is-modular-arithmetic

Link to program from video:
